data.description: Located in the heart of Royse City! This 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom and 2 car garage is close to all your amenities and minutes to Lake Ray Hubbard and everything that Royse City, Rockwall and Fate have to offer. This split bedroom floor plan offers easy living. NO HOA, P.I.D OR M.U.D.   *It’s Buyers and Buyers Agents responsibility that ALL due diligence duties and sole obligations, including following but not limited to schools, HOA, square feet, flood verification, rollback taxes, inspections, MUD or PID, surveys & appraisals, etc.***
